videos.description: Harold Cooper breaks out for a run of 24 yards in his own half.
videos.headline: Harold Cooper breaks up the sideline for 24 yards

videos.description: Rhode Island's Myles Ross makes an acrobatic interception on Central Michigan's Shane Morris.
videos.headline: Myles Ross picks off Shane Morris in the red zone

videos.description: Shane Morris finds Marcus Chapman over the middle for 34 yards with a beautiful pass.
videos.headline: Morris fires a dagger to Chapman for 34 yards

videos.description: Shane Morris finds Brandon Childress wide open for a 4-yard touchdown up the middle to put Central Michigan up 10-0.
videos.headline: Morris finds Childress for a 4-yard TD

videos.description: Tyler Harris throws a fade along the sideline to Aaron Parker for 34 yards.
videos.headline: Harris finds Parker for a 34 yard gain

videos.description: Shane Morris scrambles 14 yards and jumps over a defender for a first down.
videos.headline: Morris hurdles defender for first down

videos.description: Harold Cooper uses his speed for a 22-yard run up the right sideline.
videos.headline: Cooper scrambles up the right for 22 yards

videos.description: Isaiah Hill forces a fumble on a run from Devon Spalding, picked up by Momodou Mbye for Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Rhode Island recovers fumble

videos.description: Isaiah Coulter does most of the work on 56 yard touchdown pass from Tyler Hill, Central Michigan up 7 - 13.
videos.headline: Coulter takes it 56 yards for the TD on short pass from Harris

videos.description: Jonathan Ward runs up the middle for a 36-yard Central Michigan touchdown capped off by a Shane Morris 2-point conversion pass to Mark Chapman.
videos.headline: Ward takes it 36 yards up the middle for a TD

videos.description: Tyler Harris finds Marven Beauvais for an 80-yard touchdown pass up the middle, Central Michigan leads 21-14.
videos.headline: Harris throws an 80-yard touchdown to Beauvais

videos.description: Tyler Harris throws his 5th interception of the night, picked off by Amari Coleman for his 2nd INT of the night.
videos.headline: Harris picked off for the 5th time by CMU

videos.description: Tyler Harris ties the game with a 14-yard fade to Aaron Parker with two minutes left in the game.
videos.headline: Harris ties it with a 14-yard TD to Parker

videos.description: Devon Spalding wins the game with a 3-yard run up the middle in triple overtime, 30-27 Central Michigan.
videos.headline: Spalding wins it in 3OT for CMU
